<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="actively-adv">actively <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æktɪvli/    美 /ˈæktɪvli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>活跃地；积极地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was actively looking for a job.
她正积极找工作。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It is good for elderly people to be <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (active) involved in community service.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. actively  </p></div>